thread.title: Steven Dukes

author: Steven Dukes
title: Steven Dukes
text: I was a bit hesitate at first when I saw the price of the Windows 10 License but after reading many positive reviews I went ahead with the purchase. The license key immediately showed up via Email right after I completed the purchase and I had absolutely no trouble when I entered the license key during the Windows 10 setup. Works perfectly; will highly recommend you to others.
